        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/338/028/original/7029f1bb-37d3-4a84-8e92-b0c8ff72092f.png" srcset="" alt="Open SpeedGrader" height="78" width="282">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_47B9EA00-22D7-0135-7A2D-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Open SpeedGrader from any assignment, graded discussion, or quiz.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="B90E8163-030F-431A-B667-9C0341FA7816">
    <h2 id="open_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open SpeedGrader Options</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/338/030/original/a4a15fbf-d7d6-453a-87a5-faadbd2829ae.png" srcset="" alt="Open SpeedGrader Options" height="206" width="343">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_47BA1BB0-22D7-0135-7A2F-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Settings</strong> icon [1]. In the settings drop-down menu, click the <strong>Options </strong>link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="hide_student_names" data-step-uuid="B370C070-4AC2-4849-9CAF-60E95151C09E">
    <h2 id="hide_student_names" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Hide Student Names</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/338/032/original/d85b9f87-f0e7-4625-a8c9-50d61e629b7e.png" srcset="" alt="Hide Student Names" height="283" width="409">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_47BA4EF0-22D7-0135-7A31-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To hide the student names, click the <strong>Hide student names in the SpeedGrader </strong>checkbox.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If the checkbox to hide student names is not visible in SpeedGrader settings, anonymous grading has been enabled for the assignment. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

